cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the classification of mammogram patches using texture-based descriptors. Hence, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves feature selection techniques and classification algorithms, which are common in the sub-categories cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves the use of a standard database for testing, which is common in the sub-category cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
